Websocket poll
Poll management system using websocket.
====================================
Getting Started

1.Install the socky server gem
    	gem install socky-server
2.Install the socky-client and socky-client-rails gems
	gem install socky-client
	
	bundle install
3.Create Database
	rake db:create 
	rake db:migrate
4.Generate Rails config file:
    	rake socky:create_config
5.Generate Socky config file:
    	socky -g config/socky.yml
6.Run Socky server
    	socky -c config/socky.yml
7.Run Rails app
    	rails s
8.Point to http://localhost:3000

